setTicketCode(String) - Method in class core.Pass
Ticket's code length must be equal to Constants.TICKET_CODE_LENGTH the 3 first chars must be a letter between 'A' and 'Z' the 4 char must be '-' the last 3 chars must be a digit between '0' and '9' example for a correct ticket's code format is > 'ABC-123' , 'AAA-111' example for an incorrect ticket's code is > 'ABCD-11' , 'A2A-111', 'AA2244B' IFF the given ticket code from the constructor is not valid then the global ticketCode get null value.
